{lang-eng}Come to Bethlehem and see
Him whose birth the angels sing;
Come, adore on bended knee
Christ the Lord, the newborn king.
Glo——-ria in excelsis Deo;
Glo——-ria in excelsis Deo.{/lang-eng}
